ZH: 1. 做蠢事会让你后悔不已。
EN: 1. Doing stupid things will make you regret deeply.
ZH: 2. 他每天都会干出一些蠢事。
EN: 2. He does some stupid things every day.
ZH: 3. 不要再做那种蠢事了。
EN: 3. Don't do that kind of stupid thing again.
ZH: 4. 我真后悔刚刚那个蠢事。
EN: 4. I really regret that stupid thing I just did.
ZH: 5. 落水并不是个好主意，那是个蠢事。
EN: 5. Diving into the water is not a good idea, it's a stupid thing to do.
ZH: 6. 给别人讲这个蠢事，我真是丢脸。
EN: 6. It's embarrassing to tell others about this stupid thing.
ZH: 7. 你真是个不停干蠢事的人。
EN: 7. You're really someone who keeps doing stupid things.
ZH: 8. 这是个蠢事，你不应该去做。
EN: 8. This is a stupid thing, you shouldn't do it.
ZH: 9. 我后悔了，这个决定真是个蠢事。
EN: 9. I regret it, this decision was really a stupid thing.
ZH: 10. 他总是喜欢在别人面前做蠢事。
EN: 10. He always likes to do stupid things in front of others.
ZH: 11. 她经常为了赌博而干出一些蠢事。
EN: 11. She often does stupid things for gambling.
ZH: 12. 我不相信他会做出这样的蠢事。
EN: 12. I can't believe he would do such a stupid thing.
ZH: 13. 你已经够大了，不应该再做蠢事了。
EN: 13. You're already old enough, you shouldn't do stupid things anymore.
ZH: 14. 别把我扯进你的蠢事里。
EN: 14. Don't involve me in your stupid things.
ZH: 15. 后悔过去的蠢事是没有用的。
EN: 15. Regretting past stupid things is useless.
ZH: 16. 每次你都能干出一些奇怪的蠢事。
EN: 16. Every time you can do some strange stupid things.
ZH: 17. 别再问我那些蠢事了。
EN: 17. Stop asking me those stupid things.
ZH: 18. 这是个蠢事，我们应该避免去做。
EN: 18. This is a stupid thing, we should avoid doing it.
ZH: 19. 我们都曾经做过一些愚蠢的蠢事。
EN: 19. We have all done some stupid things.
ZH: 20. 我发誓再也不做那种蠢事了。
EN: 20. I swear I won't do that kind of stupid thing again.
